notice is that the inputs and the outputs switch for the inverse function. In

00:00:17.694 --> 00:00:21.513
other words, notice how a, b, and c were always the input for the first

00:00:21.513 --> 00:00:27.539
function we looked at. Whereas in the inverse function, a, b and c were all

00:00:27.539 --> 00:00:33.284
outputs. Another way of thinking about it is that the x and y coordinate always

00:00:33.284 --> 00:00:40.060
switched. So, here for x I had a, and for y I had 2. In the inverse function

00:00:40.060 --> 00:00:46.750
